go-to-memories: ʻAlu ki he Ko ʻEku Manatu Melié
missing_album: ʻOku ʻikai ke toe ʻi ai ha tohi tā peheni.
no-album: ʻOku ʻikai ke toe ʻi ai ha tohi tā peheni.
recently_deleted_explanation: ʻE tamateʻi ʻaupito ʻa e ngaahi manatu melie ʻi laló hili ha ʻaho ʻe 120.  Lolotonga hoʻo kei ʻi he Toki Tamateʻí, he ʻikai lava ke mamataʻi kinautolu ʻe he niʻihi kehé, fakatonutonu, pe fakapipiki ki he Fuʻu ʻAkau Fakafāmilí.
text: Lomiʻi ʻi he fakaʻilonga tānaki lanumatá ke tānaki atu ʻa e ngaahi manatu melie ki he tohi tā ko ʻení, pe tohoʻi ʻo tukuange ʻa e ngaahi manatu melié ki he tohitaá.
text-collection: Lomi‘i ʻi he fakaʻilonga tānaki lanumatá ke tānaki atu ʻa e ngaahi manatu melie ki he ngaahi meʻa kuo fakatahatahaʻi ko ʻení, pe tohoʻi ʻo tukuange ʻa e ngaahi manatu melié ki he ngaahi meʻa kuo fakatahatahaʻí.
text-mobile: Lomiʻi ʻi he fakaʻilonga tānaki lanumatá ke tānaki atu e ngaahi manatu melié ki he tohi tā ko ʻení, pe filifili ha ngaahi manatu melie mei ha tohi tā kehe.
text-mobile-collection: Lomiʻi ʻi he fakaʻilonga tānaki lanumatá ke tānaki atu ha ngaahi manatu melie ki he ngaahi meʻa ko ʻeni kuo fakatahatahaʻí, pe filifili ha ngaahi manatu melie mei ha ngaahi meʻa kuo fakatahatahaʻi kehe.
title: Kamata hono Tānaki ʻo e Ngaahi Manatu Melié.
unauth-text: ʻOku ʻikai ha meʻa ʻi he tohi tā ko ʻení.
